3. **Marmalade** (food item)  
4. **Quilt** (textile item)  
5. **Quill** (writing tool)  
6. **Quantum** (scientific concept, though borderline technical)  
7. **Sculpture** (art object)  
8. **Desert** (geographical feature)  
9. **Symphony** (musical composition)  
10. **Algorithm** (mathematical process)
